<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This item is obtained through a quest in RV.  You have to get a Grizzly Bear Skin, a Polar bear Skin, a Shark Skin, and an Alligator Skin.  I've managed to get all, but the Alligator Skin which is a rare drop from Fat, or Bull Alligators.  From what I understand this gets you a different version of the cap, but if you turn in a Dragoon Dirk with the cap, you get the real thing.</font></td></tr></table>
