<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Duffo</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-02 17:55:36</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I finally got one!!!  You have to turn in the first cap(the one obtained from turning the skins), and the Dragoon Dirk. There is another Marshal, past the stand with the Mayor, and the Sheriff. He will give you both the quest for the skins, and the Leatherfoot Raider's Cap.  When you turn the skins in, he will give you a Leatherfoot Skullcap. The ones you get in Nektulos aren't the right ones. The right one will have a +10 CHR bonus to it.<BR>
<BR>
I admit that the Dragoon Dirk is a nice weapon, but look at the stats on this compared to the Dirk.</font></td></tr></table>
