<BR>
<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Tytan</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-29 11:07:23</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have done the quest twice and here is the low down.  You talk to the marshal in a small alcove to the right of the mayor.  He will tell you to get four skins.  Alligator, polar bear, grizzly bear, and shark.  The polar bear skin is gotten in everfrost.  Polar bear cubs will drop the skin. I never had to kill more than 15 to get a skin and the cubs are all over the place up there.  The grizzly is from almost any bear in the game, grizzlies in the Karanas and I have gotten a skin from kodiaks in the Commons.  Shark skin can be bought from vendors by the seas in N. Ro or you can kill the shark that spawns between the shore and a small pillar of rock to the right of the freeport docks.  Shark is about lvl 5 maybe.  Alligator skin is from Bull Alligators only!  The Bulls are uncommon animals and the skin is a rare drop.  A good place to hunt the bulls is on the island that has the haunted tower in the swamp.  I have killed lots just standing on the shore and using the "target nearest NPC" button.  Another trick is to go to the top of the tower (kill the skeletons and possibly lesser mummy first) and wait.  Creatures will crawl up the walls of the tower and when they get to the top they cannot get over the rampart at the top so they get stuck up there.  This method is time consuming so you might want to camp there, play another character, and check back every hour or so.  I have heard stories of people buying the Alligator Skins for 300pp?!  Take the skins to the marshal, give them to him all at once and in the order he asks for them and he will give you an AC 4 version of the skullcap.  Give him that version and a Dragoon Dirk and he will give you the better AC 7 version with all the cool stat buffs.  By the way the bull alligator is about lvl 8-11.  I don't know for certain cause I did the quest with a lvl 15 warrior and he was green to me.  I plan on wearing my Skullcap even in the planes, I like it that much.<BR>
<BR>
Tytan<BR>
Xegony</font></td></tr></table>
